<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.4.3">
<l>tiruvil polinta veḻilā rāyartam piḷḷaika ḷōṭu</l>
<l>teruvil tiḷaikkiṉṟa nampī ceykiṉṟa tīmai kaḷkaṇṭiṭ</l>
<l>ṭuruki yeṉkoṅkai yiṉtīmpā lōṭṭantu pāynti ṭukiṉṟa</l>
<l>maruvik kuṭaṅkā liruntu vāymulai yuṇṇanī vārāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Prince who is playing on the road with the herders’ beautiful children</l>
<l rend="indent">who flourish in riches,</l>
<l>[When I] melt, having truly seen the mischief [you] are doing,</l>
<l>The sweet milk of my breasts flows freely, creating a flood;</l>
<l>Sitting on my lap, embracing [me], come to eat [with your] lips [at my] breast.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
